---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
export const prerender = false;
---

<PageLayout
  title="UAE–Indonesia Freight | Dubai to Jakarta Air & Sea | UKF Services"
  description="Specialist UAE–Indonesia freight forwarding. Air freight Dubai to Jakarta in 8–12 hours. Sea freight Jebel Ali to Tanjung Priok in 12–16 days. Halal cargo specialists. Get a quote today."
  image="/images/indonesia-hero.webp"
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="indo-hero">
    <div class="indo-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="indo-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container indo-hero-content">
      <div class="indo-flags">🇦🇪 → 🇮🇩</div>
      <p class="eyebrow">UAE–Indonesia Corridor</p>
      <h1 class="indo-title">Dubai to Indonesia.<br/><span class="indo-title-gold">Done Right.</span></h1>
      <p class="indo-subtitle">GCC–Indonesia bilateral trade exceeded $8B in 2024 and is accelerating. UKF has built dedicated expertise in this corridor — covering Jakarta, Batam, and Surabaya with both air and sea options.</p>
      <div class="indo-hero-ctas">
        <a href="/contact" class="indo-cta-primary">Get a Corridor Quote</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/971552572837?text=Hello%20UKF%2C%20I%27d%20like%20a%20quote%20for%20UAE%20to%20Indonesia%20freight." target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="indo-cta-wa">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
          WhatsApp for Indonesia Enquiries
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS BAR -->
  <section class="indo-stats-bar">
    <div class="container indo-stats-grid">
      <div class="indo-stat"><strong>8–12 hrs</strong><span>Dubai → Jakarta air</span></div>
      <div class="indo-stat-div"></div>
      <div class="indo-stat"><strong>12–16 days</strong><span>Jebel Ali → Tanjung Priok sea</span></div>
      <div class="indo-stat-div"></div>
      <div class="indo-stat"><strong>$8B+</strong><span>GCC–Indonesia trade 2024</span></div>
      <div class="indo-stat-div"></div>
      <div class="indo-stat"><strong>Halal</strong><span>Certified cargo specialists</span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CORRIDOR DETAIL -->
  <section class="indo-detail-section">
    <div class="container indo-detail-grid">

      <!-- MAIN -->
      <div class="indo-main fade-up">

        <!-- Air -->
        <div class="indo-mode-card">
          <div class="indo-mode-header">
            <span class="indo-mode-icon">✈</span>
            <div>
              <h2>Air Freight — Dubai to Jakarta</h2>
              <p class="indo-mode-time">Dubai (DXB) → Jakarta (CGK) · 8–12 hours flight time</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>Emirates and Garuda Indonesia operate daily direct services between Dubai International and Soekarno-Hatta International Airport. For time-sensitive cargo, air is the fastest and most reliable option on this corridor.</p>
          <div class="indo-routes-grid">
            <div class="indo-route">
              <span class="indo-route-from">Dubai DXB</span>
              <span class="indo-route-arrow">→</span>
              <span class="indo-route-to">Jakarta CGK</span>
              <span class="indo-route-time">8–12 hrs</span>
            </div>
            <div class="indo-route">
              <span class="indo-route-from">Dubai DXB</span>
              <span class="indo-route-arrow">→</span>
              <span class="indo-route-to">Surabaya SUB</span>
              <span class="indo-route-time">10–14 hrs</span>
            </div>
            <div class="indo-route">
              <span class="indo-route-from">Dubai DXB</span>
              <span class="indo-route-arrow">→</span>
              <span class="indo-route-to">Batam BTH</span>
              <span class="indo-route-time">via SIN · 12–16 hrs</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="indo-checklist">
            <li>Emirates SkyCargo and Garuda direct slot access</li>
            <li>Export documentation and UAE customs clearance managed</li>
            <li>Indonesian import documentation pre-prepared</li>
            <li>Halal cargo certification and handling where required</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Sea -->
        <div class="indo-mode-card">
          <div class="indo-mode-header">
            <span class="indo-mode-icon">🚢</span>
            <div>
              <h2>Sea Freight — Jebel Ali to Indonesia</h2>
              <p class="indo-mode-time">Jebel Ali (AEJEA) → Tanjung Priok (IDJKT) · 12–16 days</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>Jebel Ali is one of the busiest container ports in the world — and Indonesia's Tanjung Priok handles over 7 million TEUs annually. Weekly sailings with MSC, CMA CGM, and Evergreen on this corridor make sea freight a reliable, cost-effective option for bulk cargo.</p>
          <div class="indo-routes-grid">
            <div class="indo-route">
              <span class="indo-route-from">Jebel Ali</span>
              <span class="indo-route-arrow">→</span>
              <span class="indo-route-to">Tanjung Priok (Jakarta)</span>
              <span class="indo-route-time">12–16 days</span>
            </div>
            <div class="indo-route">
              <span class="indo-route-from">Jebel Ali</span>
              <span class="indo-route-arrow">→</span>
              <span class="indo-route-to">Tanjung Perak (Surabaya)</span>
              <span class="indo-route-time">14–18 days</span>
            </div>
            <div class="indo-route">
              <span class="indo-route-from">Jebel Ali</span>
              <span class="indo-route-arrow">→</span>
              <span class="indo-route-to">Batam (via Singapore)</span>
              <span class="indo-route-time">10–14 days</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="indo-checklist">
            <li>FCL and LCL options — full and groupage containers</li>
            <li>Weekly sailings with MSC, CMA CGM, Evergreen</li>
            <li>Bill of Lading and full export documentation managed</li>
            <li>Batam Free Trade Zone expertise for re-export cargo</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Halal -->
        <div class="indo-mode-card indo-mode-card--gold">
          <div class="indo-mode-header">
            <span class="indo-mode-icon">🌙</span>
            <div>
              <h2>Halal Cargo Specialists</h2>
              <p class="indo-mode-time">Indonesia is the world's largest Muslim-majority nation</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>Indonesia's import regulations for food, pharmaceuticals, and cosmetics require halal certification and specific documentation from Indonesian authorities (MUI, BPJPH). We navigate this documentation framework as standard — not as a special exception.</p>
          <ul class="indo-checklist">
            <li>Halal certification documentation guidance</li>
            <li>BPJPH and MUI import permit coordination</li>
            <li>Food and cosmetic import regulatory compliance</li>
            <li>Segregated handling where halal integrity is required</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Customs -->
        <div class="indo-mode-card">
          <div class="indo-mode-header">
            <span class="indo-mode-icon">📋</span>
            <div>
              <h2>Indonesian Customs — Red Lane Navigation</h2>
              <p class="indo-mode-time">Indonesian customs has green, yellow, and red channels</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>Indonesian customs is notoriously complex — with a risk-based inspection system (green/yellow/red lane) that can delay cargo significantly if documentation is incomplete or incorrect. We prepare every shipment to minimise red lane risk from the outset.</p>
          <ul class="indo-checklist">
            <li>HS code verification for Indonesian tariff schedules</li>
            <li>Lartas (import restriction) compliance checks</li>
            <li>Pre-shipment inspection coordination where required</li>
            <li>Customs agent coordination at Tanjung Priok and Priok</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- SIDEBAR -->
      <aside class="indo-sidebar">
        <div class="indo-sidebar-card indo-sidebar-card--navy fade-up">
          <h3>Get an Indonesia Quote</h3>
          <p>Tell us your cargo details and destination port — we'll respond same day.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="indo-sidebar-btn">Request Corridor Quote</a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/971552572837?text=Hello%20UKF%2C%20I%27d%20like%20a%20quote%20for%20UAE%20to%20Indonesia." target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="indo-sidebar-wa">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="16" height="16"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
            WhatsApp for Indonesia
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="indo-sidebar-card fade-up">
          <h3>Key Indonesia Ports</h3>
          <div class="indo-ports">
            <div class="indo-port">
              <strong>Tanjung Priok</strong>
              <span>Jakarta — main commercial port</span>
            </div>
            <div class="indo-port">
              <strong>Tanjung Perak</strong>
              <span>Surabaya — East Java hub</span>
            </div>
            <div class="indo-port">
              <strong>Batam</strong>
              <span>Free Trade Zone — Singapore corridor</span>
            </div>
            <div class="indo-port">
              <strong>Patimban</strong>
              <span>New port — automotive & industrial</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="indo-sidebar-card fade-up">
          <h3>Indonesia Intelligence</h3>
          <div class="indo-articles">
            <a href="/articles/halal-logistics-gcc-indonesia" class="indo-article-link">Halal Logistics: GCC to Indonesia Guide →</a>
            <a href="/articles/indonesia-customs-red-lane-guide" class="indo-article-link">Indonesia Customs Red Lane Guide →</a>
            <a href="/articles/jebel-ali-tanjung-priok-sea-freight" class="indo-article-link">Jebel Ali to Tanjung Priok: Sea Freight →</a>
            <a href="/articles/dubai-jakarta-air-corridor" class="indo-article-link">Dubai–Jakarta Air Corridor Guide →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="indo-cta-section fade-up">
    <div class="container indo-cta-inner">
      <div>
        <h2>Ready to ship to Indonesia?</h2>
        <p>Speak to our Indonesia corridor specialists today.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="indo-cta-btns">
        <a href="/contact" class="indo-cta-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/971552572837" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="indo-cta-wa">WhatsApp Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JSON-LD -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Service",
    "name": "UAE-Indonesia Freight Forwarding",
    "description": "Specialist air and sea freight between the UAE and Indonesia - Jakarta, Surabaya, and Batam - with halal cargo expertise and Indonesian customs clearance.",
    "provider": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "UKF Services", "url": "https://ukfservices.com" },
    "areaServed": ["AE", "ID"],
    "url": "https://ukfservices.com/services/indonesia"
  }
  </script>

</PageLayout>

<style>
  .eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }

  /* HERO */
  .indo-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .indo-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: url('/images/indonesia-hero.webp') center/cover no-repeat;
    opacity: 0.15;
  }
  .indo-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10,22,40,0.97) 0%, rgba(15,42,80,0.92) 100%);
  }
  .indo-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .indo-flags { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: 8px; }
  .indo-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 68px);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .indo-title-gold { color: var(--gold); }
  .indo-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 18px);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 36px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .indo-hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .indo-cta-primary { background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy); font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 6px; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
  .indo-cta-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .indo-cta-wa { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: #25D366; color: #fff; font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; padding: 13px 24px; border-radius: 6px; transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
  .indo-cta-wa:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  /* STATS */
  .indo-stats-bar { background: var(--navy); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2); padding: 32px 0; }
  .indo-stats-grid { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .indo-stat { text-align: center; padding: 8px 32px; }
  .indo-stat strong { display: block; font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .indo-stat span { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
  .indo-stat-div { width: 1px; height: 36px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  @media (max-width: 700px) { .indo-stat-div { display: none; } }

  /* DETAIL */
  .indo-detail-section { padding: 64px 0 80px; background: var(--gray-100); }
  .indo-detail-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px; gap: 40px; align-items: start; }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) { .indo-detail-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .indo-main { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 28px; }
  .indo-mode-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 36px;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .indo-mode-card--gold { border-top-color: var(--gold); background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffdf5 0%, #fff 100%); }
  .indo-mode-header { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .indo-mode-icon { font-size: 32px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px; }
  .indo-mode-header h2 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 22px; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .indo-mode-time { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }
  .indo-mode-card > p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 20px; }

  .indo-routes-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .indo-route {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--gray-100);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .indo-route-from { font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); }
  .indo-route-arrow { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }
  .indo-route-to { color: var(--gray-600); }
  .indo-route-time { font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); text-align: right; white-space: nowrap; }

  .indo-checklist { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .indo-checklist li { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-600); padding-left: 22px; position: relative; line-height: 1.5; }
  .indo-checklist li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }

  /* SIDEBAR */
  .indo-sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; position: sticky; top: 100px; }
  .indo-sidebar-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; }
  .indo-sidebar-card--navy { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-mid) 100%); border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.2); }
  .indo-sidebar-card h3 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 18px; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .indo-sidebar-card--navy h3 { color: var(--white); }
  .indo-sidebar-card p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-600); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .indo-sidebar-card--navy p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }
  .indo-sidebar-btn { display: block; background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy); text-align: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .indo-sidebar-btn:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }
  .indo-sidebar-wa { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; background: #25D366; color: #fff; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
  .indo-sidebar-wa:hover { opacity: 0.9; }

  .indo-ports { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .indo-port { padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-100); }
  .indo-port:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .indo-port strong { display: block; font-size: 14px; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .indo-port span { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-400); }

  .indo-articles { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .indo-article-link { display: block; font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-600); padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-100); transition: color 0.2s; }
  .indo-article-link:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .indo-article-link:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  /* CTA */
  .indo-cta-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0f2a50 100%); padding: 64px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2); }
  .indo-cta-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .indo-cta-inner h2 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 32px); color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .indo-cta-inner p { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
  .indo-cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
</style>
